<p>Also, the region could be an exclusion zone for some other reason - it might be near where <em>Kursk</em> went down. In real life all <em>Kursk</em>'s weapons were recovered, but suppose they weren't, and she did indeed have some nuke-tipped P-700 Granit rounds aboard…</p>
